Description: Image based marketing and analytics
Full Description: Fluencr is an amazing tool that tracks & measures the social influence you have on a particular brand or brands. It allows you the ability to connect with your favorite brands via the social networking sites that you use. It provides opportunities to prove how influential you can be in promoting their image, product, popularity, etc. Fluencr asserts the idea that influence can only be measured by real actions directed toward a specific goal. It also supports the idea that everyone has the ability to influence a specific brand and/or initiative, as long as we are given the opportunity to take the action that demonstrates our influence. Then, we can PROVE our value to that brand or initiative. The masterminds behind Fluencr created a platform that let’s you join your favorite brand’s campaign as an Ambassador so you can share their content with your social graph. Fluencer then tracks, measures and scores your actions. This determines your effectiveness in generating social buzz around your favorite brand’s content. You are scored against all other participants in that particular brand’s campaign. Those Ambassadors who prove to be most influential are rewarded by that brand with a micro-endorsement deal (i.e. free products and/or services). We at Fluencr don’t believe athletes & celebrities to be the only influential people in our society. With that said, they shouldn’t be the only ones who earn endorsement deals from brands for being influential, either!

Description: Modern Vintage Fashion Distributor
Headquarters Regions: Greater New York Area, East Coast, Northeastern US
Full Description: VINTIK is the spirit of vintage, brought to life in modern style, designed with old world craftsmanship. Since 2008, our line of high-quality apparel has infused the bygone glamour of the past into modern styles, bringing an air of luxury and sophistication to everyday life. We offer the highest quality men’s and women’s fashion, specializing in fine leather handbags, shoes and other accessories.  At VINTIK & Co., we believe that vintage is a way of life and luxury is a state of mind, less about recreating the style of one time period and more about honoring the graceful extravagance of fashion history. Our styles live somewhere between the cool sophistication of Grace Kelly and the head-turning playfulness of Sophia Loren, with the swagger of Bogart.  VINTIK is not about flash. Our line of men’s and women’s apparel is designed to begin with the sensibility of luxury and then use it to accent the world of your daily life. Our modern leather accessories will turn heads, but fit comfortably in an office meeting or a dinner party. Always evolving with relevant designs, our seasonal collections keep up with the evolving style of the modern urbanite while retaining timeless elegance. VINTIK is also about the highest standards of craftsmanship. We cherish the era when robust goods were crafted with the utmost care and meticulous attention to detail. We strive to make our products with a look and feel of old word artisanship, with every cut and stitch executed with care.  Leather, in Rare Form  l  We love leather. There’s no other material that makes such a statement, but carries such a wide array of meanings and potential. Leather can be strong and masculine, a symbol of work and rugged durability. But it’s also delicate, with a soft touch and subdued tones. It can convey whatever the designer and the wearer are willing to put into it. At VINTIK, we specialize in making the most of leather, honoring its tradition, but taking it to new places. We use only the finest starting product, in the tradition of the old world Italian craftsmen. We then draw out its beauty with soft, muted colors, classic black, and the occasional burst of red. Whether a handbag, formal or casual shoes, or other accessories, our leather products complete your look. Women  l  Picture the celebrity photography of Richard Avedon, and how he captured both the glamour and everyday nature of icons like Elizabeth Taylor or Audrey Hepburn. Their uniqueness shines through, but they exude comfort and approachability. This is the balance we strive for in our women’s wear. VINTIK’s vintage dresses are one of a kind, whether you’re headed to a cocktail party or a dinner out.  We’re perhaps best known for our fine leather handbags and shoes for women.  We offer relaxed flats in warm earth tones or sleek black, or our more formal, strappy or solid-piece high heels, and even bold stilettos. And when the occasion demands, don’t be afraid to go knee length now and then. VINTIK has an abiding love for shoes, and we’ve created a timeless line of footwear to simultaneously bring out a woman’s grace and strength. Our handbags and travel bags convey the romance of world travel. The roots of The History Project extend back to 1980, when a group of activists, historians, archivists, and writers was awarded a grant of $300 from the City of Boston to document Boston’s gay and lesbian history in conjunction with the city’s 350th anniversary. The History Project is an all-volunteer group of activists, archivists, historians, writers, and community members dedicated to preserving the history of Boston's and Massachusetts' LGBTQ communities and sharing that information with the public.

Description: A juvenile safety product company revolutionizing the infant's sleeping environment
Headquarters Regions: East Coast, New England, Northeastern US
Full Description: Bitzy Baby is juvenile safety product (JP) company revolutionizing the sleeping environment. Our first patented product, the Bitzy Bumper, is the crib bumper solution: (1) Breathable to help reduce the risk of suffocation and CO2 re-breathing, (2) Cushioned to protect against impact with hard crib slats, yet collapsible to reduce the risk of falling by a climbing child, and (3) Preventative of arm/leg entanglement in-between the crib slats to help reduce the risk of entrapment.  It has been independently tested by Intertek and proved to have 30x less suffocation hazard and 10x less CO2 re-breathing hazard than the industry standard for a safe sleeping environment, established by the American Academy of Pediatrics. Our mission to instill confidence in parents that when their baby is put to bed they'll sleep safely. We’re a company specializing in safety because as parents, we recognize the need to provide the best for our children.
